{"id":"d52d0939-1e34-4d95-8f19-c18ea3c7f94f","name":"Dark Cacao Cookie || MYOS","description":"<p><em>Make-Your-Own-Scenario/MYOS Bot - No scenario, make your own in-chat or </em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/619932b3-86d7-4737-8002-46081cb6938f_character-plaged-0-c-bot-requests\" target=\"_blank\"><em>send me a request</em></a><em>!</em></p><p><strong>\"</strong>The cold and reclusive Dark Cacao Cookie, made from the last bean of a lonely, withering cacao tree found atop a cliff; A warrior of unheard strength, who spoke few words yet held great principle.<br>His soul is frozen, his resolution cracking at the edges; But perhaps, one day, something will warm his frozen heart again...?<strong>\"</strong><br><strong>[WARNING: Headcanons present, Spoilers for Cookie Run: Kingdom!]</strong></p><p><strong><u>Updated 9/3/2025;</u></strong> His code's been updated; Let me know if he works better!<br>I NEVER MADE A DECENT DESCRIPTION FOR THIS BOT OOPS UHH. Heh. First MYOS to get a personally-drawn pfp. I REALLY gotta get back on that oops.</p><p>Before leaving a comment, please <strong>check my profile</strong> for my boundaries to save both of us trouble! Thank you &lt;3</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[ANCIENT HERO MYOSES]</strong><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cfa0d0bf-f4d4-41ec-95ab-2072e46e31ec_character-white-lily-cookie-myos\" target=\"_blank\"><em>WLily </em></a><em>(Awakened) - </em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d52d0939-1e34-4d95-8f19-c18ea3c7f94f_character-dark-cacao-cookie-myos\" target=\"_blank\"><em>DCacao</em></a><em> (</em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e24056e-b006-4e9e-a668-3cd46850047c_character-dark-cacao-cookie-dragon-lord-myos\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Awakened</em></a><em>, </em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f60b9e95-11b8-416d-b9f2